race.comment: WEBLEC BILLY (2) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts three wins. Missed the frame latest (30.66) when fourth over 525m at The Meadows in a Grade 5 H. Looks the one to beat with even luck. VINCENT BALE (4) flew the lids from out wide with a slick early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (34.52) over 600m at The Meadows. Has ability and is one of the better chances. GIACOMO (1) goes very well this trip starting 28 times for 11 wins and eight minors. Below best last time at this track (29.69) in a Special conditions H, finishing a 6 length sixth. Can feature in the finish. BLAME HER (7) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.
